{"tid":149367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊中東情侶 旅行期間睇醫生證有咗 涉未婚懷孕被捕","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:43:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T07:53:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adcef39fbd2a9e8829ad032b73eaad74c1c8a4d8","tid":149367,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489034372_52a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489034372_52a7.jpg&h=05df39f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489034373_bb4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489034373_bb4d.jpg&h=d3b45e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489034374_a958.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489034374_a958.jpg&h=6323b1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旅行本來是開心事，在旅行期間發現懷孕更加是喜上加喜，一對情侶遊阿聯酋時發現懷孕，卻被當局以進行婚前性行為被捕，面臨牢獄之災。<br />\n<br />\n來自南非的27歲孕婦諾哈伊（Iryna Nohai）與29歲來自烏克蘭的未婚夫卡爾弗韋爾（Emlyn Culverwell）本來享受美好假期，但諾哈伊突然胃痛，於是與未婚夫去醫院，醫院發現她懷孕後，便通知警方稱兩人仍未結婚。<br />\n<br />\n婚前性行為在阿聯酋屬刑事罪行，兩人被捕後卡爾弗韋爾的媽媽琳達（Linda）很擔心。琳達指烏克蘭使館正嘗試尋求批准為兩人圓婚，或是一同被遞解出鏡。<br />\n<br />\n琳達又透露儘管目前阿聯酋名當局未有提正式起訴，但諾哈伊卻要接受檢查，查清她究竟幾時開始性生活活躍，「天啊！他們要如何決定這些事？她一定覺得自己被政府強暴。」<br />\n<br />\n由於諾哈伊目前仍屬懷孕初期，琳達很擔心她的胃痛是流產跡象，並形容這是「地獄」般情況，「所有外交機構都叫我們要有耐性，但這就有三條人命啊。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403323&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403323%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9osmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=7efb3869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170309%26guid%3D56403323%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=2de03d26\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170309&amp;guid=56403323&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"6ed8200516b6ad99532731594db58789e8ac80fb","tid":149367,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"用石頭擲死她!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"6f3d4f31bccb13b084e6ae8c61ef6c75387b7d0f","tid":149367,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"女權鬥士Emma Watson幾時去中東呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中東啲女人好需要幫有人佢哋發聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa81846d308172e4b6f4d6abee95d0e96b26edb","tid":149367,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a4d9e800f8b7927c2d2a8deb04146a1ed57b99","tid":149367,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女權鬥士Emma Watson幾時去中東呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中東啲女人好需要幫有人佢哋發聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ntopic係未婚懷孕, 內文係婚前性行為, 一入境俾人驗西即刻拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3a4bcea0c946d0cada00d35ec80727c041fa51","tid":149367,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:54:49.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 洗唔洗結婚證先買得condom"},{"pid":"4870f07c00d2d31cf15219f87bd6c361f59f908e","tid":149367,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:48:56.00